{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layout to add in your views a lonely checkbox, without labels, texts nor icons components."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you want to use a checkbox with additional texts and icon, prefer instead "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox\/init(isOn:accessibilityLabel:isError:)"],"title":"Initializers"},{"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox\/body"],"title":"Instance Properties"},{"generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox\/View-Implementations"],"title":"Default Implementations"}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents12OUDSCheckboxV","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckbox","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSCheckbox","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"OUDSCheckbox","symbolKind":"struct"},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckbox"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckbox"}]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Indicator states","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Indicator-states"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This checkbox indicator has two available states:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"selected","type":"text"}]},{"text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you need to use a tri-state checkbox instead, refer to "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Particular cases","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Particular-cases"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Accessibility considerations","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for checkbox.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Cases forbidden by design","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Code samples","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples"},{"code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have a selected checkbox","    @Published var isOn: Bool = true","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, but is an error context","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckbox(isOn: $isOn, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"text":"Suggestions","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Suggestions"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"According to the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/09d860-checkbox\/t\/14bf4bd854","isActive":true},{"text":", the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Design documentation","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Design-documentation"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/09d860-checkbox"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Themes rendering","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Themes-rendering"},{"text":"Orange","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_enabled_selected_Orange"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Orange Business Tools","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_enabled_selected_OrangeBusinessTools"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Orange Inverse","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Inverse"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkbox_enabled_selected_OrangeInverse","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Sosh","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Sosh"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_enabled_selected_Sosh"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Wireframe","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Wireframe"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_enabled_selected_Wireframe"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Version","type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"2.0.0 (Figma component design version)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"Since","type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0.12.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"hierarch